---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import ownerImage from '../assets/owner.jpg';
import { firm } from '../data/site';
---

<section class="section">
	<div class="shell spotlight-grid">
		<div class="portrait-card">
			<div class="portrait-frame">
				<Image
					src={ownerImage}
					alt="Tracy A. Cinocca"
					widths={[360, 520, 720]}
					sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 34vw"
					loading="lazy"
					format="avif"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="portrait-caption">
				<strong>Tracy A. Cinocca, J.D.</strong>
				<span>{firm.serviceArea}</span>
				<span>{firm.fullAddress}</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="band">
			<p class="eyebrow">Meet Tracy</p>
			<h2 class="section-title">A clear, steady point of contact from Tulsa for serious legal matters.</h2>
			<p class="lead">
				People usually reach out because they want a straight answer, a clear next step, or help
				getting important paperwork right before the situation gets more expensive or more stressful.
			</p>
			<ul class="checklist">
				<li>Direct attorney-led review for new matters</li>
				<li>Tulsa office near Bixby and Broken Arrow with statewide Oklahoma service</li>
				<li>Clear communication about fit, timing, and what should happen next</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="quote" style="margin-top: 18px;">
				From Tracy: "Most people contact me because they want to know whether the matter is worth
				pursuing, what it is likely to take, and what should happen next."
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
